A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a frustrated office worker in a retro computing room, surrounded by towering filing cabinets with drawers exploding open, index cards and punch cards cascading chaotically through the air like a paper avalanche. The worker sits at a large mid-century mainframe console with spinning tape reels frozen mid-spin, one reel visibly cracked. Muted olive greens, burnt oranges, and cream colors dominate the palette. The scene conveys technological breakdown and administrative chaos, with a single wilting potted plant on a nearby desk adding to the sense of defeat.
